{"tid":296384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍公屋新移民婦：我日日瞓晏覺，好舒服","createTime":"2017-06-24T13:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T11:27:34.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":180,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b3a515bf74b221e3b405dc9d2dd79d5a97799c0","tid":296384,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170615/2_519748_0/-%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E5%8C%97%E5%A6%B9-%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F-%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%AE%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E5%8F%AB%E5%A5%BDHea-%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%A9%A6-%E6%88%91%E6%97%A5%E6%97%A5%E7%9E%93%E6%99%8F%E8%A6%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170615%2F2_519748_0%2F-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%25A6%25B9-%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%25A6%258F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%25A5%25BDHea-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A9%25A6-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%259E%2593%25E6%2599%258F%25E8%25A6%25BA&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9b5bca3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170615%2F2_519748_0%2F-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%25A6%25B9-%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%25A6%258F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%25A5%25BDHea-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A9%25A6-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%259E%2593%25E6%2599%258F%25E8%25A6%25BA&h=f786f45b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170615/2_519748_0/-%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E5%8C%97%E5%A6%B9-%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F-%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%AE%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E5%8F%AB%E5%A5%BDHea-%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%A9%A6-%E6%88%91%E6%97%A5%E6%97%A5%E7%9E%93%E6%99%8F%E8%A6%BA</a><img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170613/large/1497343595_dd0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170613%2Flarge%2F1497343595_dd0d.jpg&h=a086e420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天水圍是吸納最多新移民，公屋圍繞着操國語的婦人交談，本刊訪問了多名嫁來港的新移民，發表來港的生活感受。 <br />\n<br />\n馬太跟港男丈夫年齡雖然相距十七年，但無損感情，她大讚丈夫為人誠實，勤力工作能吃苦，相識初期已坦白告知任職地盤，她認為一個男人不在乎有無金錢，勤力上進最為重要，「就算有錢人賺一百萬亦未必比錢你洗，他賺錢少，全部交晒比我已很足夠。」現時三口子蝸居於寶田村一人單位，樂觀的她仍很享受一家人相處的時光，「中午回家午睡，好舒服，下午接兒子放學後跟進功課，晚上煮飯比老公食，每一天過得很好！」 <br />\n<br />\n袁小姐來港多年，已適應香港的節奏，她最欣賞香港的文化、生活水平及治安，，她很滿意現時的生活，並寄語：「希望每個人都似我一樣，家庭唔需要太富有，平淡是福，生活過得舒適已足夠。」她憶述當年輪候公屋較現在快，只需輪候約五至六年便能調遷較大型的單住。 <br />\n<br />\n曾太來港已有七年，她認為香港相比大陸安全，在大陸會很擔心拐子佬捉偷小孩；同時亦很珍惜香港仍存在的言論自由，可隨時發表自己想表達的事情。"},{"pid":"db25a55d9ab26a96b7c482311171367f3800fe05","tid":296384,"uid":45232,"like":53,"dislike":4,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"其實呢D先係正常生活<br />\n但點解我地呢啲土生土長既要過地獄生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3020c9f5704859764e9db66a8216c0e4c78fb8d7","tid":296384,"uid":20058,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢D先係正常生活<br />\n但點解我地呢啲土生土長既要過地獄生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師奶10個有八個都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356dc6e85230848c0014b737147f06710aa7c522","tid":296384,"uid":48631,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢D先係正常生活<br />\n但點解我地呢啲土生土長既要過地獄生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔辛苦交稅邊個養佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7ce1a885dc905